        CLI Alarm Clock
        ===============
        
        Alarm is CLI utility written in Python language.
        
        Requirements
        ------------
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            - Python 2 or 3
            - Mplayer
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        Using `pip <https://pip.pypa.io/en/latest/>`_ :
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            $ pip install slpkg
        
            uninstall:
        
            $ pip uninstall slpkg
           
        
        Command Line Tool Usage
        -----------------------
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            usage: alarm [-h] [-v]
                         [-s] <time> <song>
        
            optional arguments
              -h, --help       show this help message and exit
              -v, --version    print version and exit
              -s, --set        set time and sound
            
            example: alarm -s 06:00:00 /path/to/song.mp3
        
        
        Example:
        
        .. code-block:: bash
            
            $ alarm -s 05:40:12 /home/dslackw/Music/xristina.ogg
        
            +==============================================================================+
            |                              CLI Alarm Clock                                 |
            +==============================================================================+
            | Alarm set at : 05:49:12                                                      |
            | Sound file in : /home/dslackw/Music/xristina.ogg                             |
            | Time : 05:17:40                                                              |
            +==============================================================================+
